Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.85,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.73,0:00:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.33,0:00:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.34,0:00:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.05,0:00:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.75,0:00:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.66,0:00:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.03,0:00:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.04,0:01:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.21,0:01:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.57,0:01:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.25,0:01:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.89,0:01:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.22,0:01:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.70,0:01:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.02,0:02:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.35,0:02:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你把這個交給響子,好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.19,0:02:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說這個東西放在我這裡\N還不如放在響子那裡比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是惣一郎的舊日記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.38,0:02:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要轉交這種東西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.95,0:02:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把日記交給管理員的話\N她一定又會想起她老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要交給她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.70,0:03:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#33 日記的衝擊!\N惣一郎有女朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,妳還沒睡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞋櫃亂七八糟的,想整理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.08,0:05:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是四谷的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來得好晚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去車站前的柏青哥店\N所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要晚回來的話\N記得請打個電話回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還得負責關門呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.04,0:06:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.54,0:06:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.21,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎麼了?\N怎麼無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.68,0:06:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要嘆氣嘆得這麼消沈啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.32,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣連健全的我們\N都會跟著你變得憂鬱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們這樣叫憂鬱嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.93,0:07:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑到人家房裡歡鬧\N這樣哪裡叫憂鬱?你說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.64,0:07:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨妒的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.41,0:07:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你對管理員做了什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是接下來要做囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我什麼都不會做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.92,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你瞞得了我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很煩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.13,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得\N我真能對管理員做什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本什麼都做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.27,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是\N你這個人本來就沒啥骨氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒出息的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.47,0:07:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.77,0:07:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛快快地喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒骨氣,沒出息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好\N是個曬衣服的好日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太\N妳家不用洗衣服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天再一起洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.46,0:09:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了\N啊,五代,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實昨天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.54,0:09:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個東西要轉交給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸託你交給我的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.55,0:09:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是什麼東西呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你過來一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啦,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對管理員做了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想瞞我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那是什麼眼神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒做什麼見不得人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到底是什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.65,0:10:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把音無老伯要我轉交給\N管理員的日記給了她而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日記?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.93,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到惣一郎有寫日記的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好是和我認識的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有寫到我的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.32,0:10:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎是在什麼時候\N開始注意到我的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.73,0:10:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七月八日\N今天是很特別的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼特別的日子\N一輩子可能只有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上在家裡吃了味噌煮青花魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了學校\N校長又請我吃味噌煮青花魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到晚上回到家一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.11,0:11:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為早上吃完的味噌煮青花魚\N居然還有剩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果今天三餐都吃味噌煮青花魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.52,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管是巧合\N這還真是令人難以置信的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七月九日,烤竹莢魚\N蘿蔔泥、草菇味噌湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.47,0:11:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七月十二日\N炸蝦,蝦子太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.67,0:11:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七月十五日\N鮭魚生魚片,涼拌菠菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.11,0:11:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七月十六日,咖哩飯\N還是中辣比較好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.72,0:11:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七月十八日\N山菜飯,實力測驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.12,0:11:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是日記嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只沒有寫到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.46,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連學校的事也幾乎沒有提到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她寄了一張這樣的明信片給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明信片呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.29,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從昨天一直想到現在\N還是搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該給她回信嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.70,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是對我而言\N這種狀況還是頭一遭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.51,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯的事連半行都沒寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰寄的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八月二日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.32,0:12:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.95,0:12:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今我一直把精神放在書本上\N從未多看女性一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.16,0:13:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到這種明信片\N我真的不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連飯都吃不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我寄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.13,0:13:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有寄過這種\N會讓他如此煩惱的明信片給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.61,0:13:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道,他除了我以外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.43,0:14:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候,惣一郎27歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.20,0:14:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有女朋友才奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明信片到哪裡去了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能在爸爸那裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,11點了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了打電話去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在很沒禮貌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.48,0:15:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對,反正都是過去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響了五聲,如果沒人接就掛斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,這裡是音無家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,響子,日記收到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.59,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說差不多可以交給妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說妳應該已經能冷靜地看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.73,0:15:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你看過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.44,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到一半就看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,明信片呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明信片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,明信片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明信片怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.98,0:16:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒事,打擾你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.04,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明信片會不會掉在五代那裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一付無精打采的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.83,0:16:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了\N今天也要去學校睡覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去是唸書的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了日記之後\N她果然想起她老公了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可千萬不要介意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我才沒有介意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.15,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的表情讓人覺得我很介意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.39,0:17:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋\N我有露出這種表情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.66,0:17:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我真的不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見,我去上學囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,是明信片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.72,0:17:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你窮到連午飯都吃不起了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.39,0:18:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,我在煩惱的\N才不是那種俗不可耐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.06,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不然是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.76,0:18:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說,聽好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.33,0:18:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說你最愛的女朋友\N遭到不幸過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過了不久\N你發現她生前的日記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.77,0:18:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面寫滿了\N兩人幸福甜蜜的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了之後,你會有什麼感想?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.05,0:18:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員她老公的日記出現了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不跟你講任何事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.41,0:18:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,這樣就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.53,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是鼓起勇氣問問看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.25,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代還沒回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四…四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫五代看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉在你的包包裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我沒有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.94,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我寫的明信片嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.04,0:21:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到這樣的明信片\N我真的很煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我居然寫過這麼\N意味深長的明信片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.59,0:21:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你看了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.03,0:22:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是明信片,很容易看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.97,0:22:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意看的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.50,0:22:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就看到了,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.84,0:22:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.58,0:22:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.34,0:22:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.75,0:22:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.31,0:22:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請好好用功唸書喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.73,0:23:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對管理員做了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.77,0:23:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把明信片還給她而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.77,0:23:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來惣一郎\N從很久以前就喜歡我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.44,0:23:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那麼簡單的一張明信片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.58,0:23:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓他那麼地煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.89,0:23:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(盛夏之際向您問候)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.97,0:23:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代的奶奶突然到東京來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.48,0:23:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還跟我、五代\N三個人一起去三鷹家玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.92,0:23:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.75,0:24:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「戀愛必須強硬!\N由加里奶奶以金牙決勝負」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.62,0:24:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來奶奶的名字叫由加里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.11,0:24:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.02,0:24:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.93,0:24:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.03,0:24:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.14,0:25:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.88,0:25:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
